        "new_rules_in_this_unit": [
            "Form adjectives from nouns by adding the suffix -los (meaning \"without\"): Wort → wortlos; add -n before -los for nouns ending in unstressed -e (Pause → pausenlos), and -s for certain nouns (Arbeit → arbeitslos)."
